=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I want to make two more points about the SPARC structu=
re. One is that, because it has no money, it really puts an emphasis on the=
 sponsor=E2=80=99s ability to do a good deal, sell that deal, and raise mon=
ey. In the SPAC boom of earlier this year, lots of random people raised SPA=
