 =E2=80=9Chey we have a pot of money here, would you like it,=E2=80=9D the =
target will be tempted to say yes. This is true even though the SPAC doesn=
=E2=80=99t <em>really</em> have a pot of money; the SPAC shareholders can t=
ake their money out before the deal closes.=C2=A0With a SPARC, on the other=
